Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:11.93,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Get off your butts and start doing damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:13.99,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Up the tempo, and whittle down his health!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:20.37,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Defeating him and solving the \Nproblem are different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:26.58,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fortress Stance!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.07,0:00:31.63,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Time to see what my new \Nshield and armor can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:35.30,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Wish strongly, and keep thinking \Nto make it come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:38.14,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Continue to train, without giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:41.14,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,These are the lessons we must hand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:43.03,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:44.77,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe's team will lead the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:47.38,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:49.60,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,500 dogs is a lucky sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.60,0:00:52.82,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get this excitement in real life!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:54.70,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:57.41,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,William, defeat the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.88,0:01:01.95,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,The bigger the pinch you overcome,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:04.96,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,the better the food tastes after!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:41.76,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys love pumpkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:47.28,SignB,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2B386F&}Guild vs. Guild \N{\c&HBE8430&}After-Halloween \N{\c&H3D2FB6&}Athletic Meet!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.45,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We sure do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:48.10,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We swear on our guild master's glasses \Nand Takayama's "good work" card
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.64,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,that we will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:52.27,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,D.D.D.!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:03:00.53,Committee,M,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1710,1)}Planning \NCommittee
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.39,0:02:55.09,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:58.64,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're on the planning committee. \NYou stay here and work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:04.53,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No! I want to play tug-of-war, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:10.54,Title,M,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1753,1)}Shiroe of the Northern Lands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:07.55,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe of the Northern Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.54,0:03:12.79,SignA,M,0000,0000,0000,,After-Halloween Planning Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:16.32,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why "After-Halloween"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:18.55,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the Halloween event?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:20.53,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:23.47,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The one held during the last three days of October,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:28.18,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,where monsters drop pumpkins when defeated, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:32.25,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,So, since we ended up with too many pumpkins,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:34.94,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,we decided to do something with them as a prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:38.18,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Marielle the strategist thinks of everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:39.94,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Air glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.49,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:46.33,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Akihabara has become so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:48.18,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:51.71,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,We were suddenly sent to a world \Nexactly like a video game,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:54.04,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,and we decided we had to do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:56.00,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,so we founded the Round Table.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:04:00.84,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,There were all kinds of things we'd never \Nget to experience in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.93,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone truly worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:08.73,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Including Serara.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.43,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Using your hands is against the rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:13.44,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And if you drop the bun, you pay for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:18.88,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Win and have a pumpkin party with Nyanta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:22.03,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Win and have a pumpkin party with Nyanta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:24.41,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,And Tohya and Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:27.12,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Tohya, don't just fling it as hard as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:30.00,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,You need to watch how the phantoms move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:30.62,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:33.50,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:36.39,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And Isuzu and Rudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.39,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:41.45,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,In the face of teamwork like ours,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a race where we have to \Nsynchronize our timing is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:48.21,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's already started!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.21,0:04:49.14,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:58.76,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is the obstacle course?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:04:59.76,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Nice fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:01.24,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:01.94,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,She's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.76,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,In first place is Akatsuki, from Log Horizon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:09.47,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win this fight, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.83,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:20.69,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I wish little Shiro and the rest could've participated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:22.71,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:25.83,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a lot to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:27.47,Location,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(385,1019)\an7}Guild Building{\fs18}\NJapan Server \NAkihabara \NCity/ No Monsters \NNo PVP \NEntry Restrictions/ None \NExit Restrictions/ None
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:27.19,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:29.43,Location,M,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(378,1)\an9}Underground Corridor{\fs18}\NJapan Server \NAkihabara \NSeparate Zone/ No Monsters \NNo PVP \NEntry Restrictions/ None \NExit Restrictions/ None
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.63,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,They're just armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:35.41,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:37.06,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:39.27,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,They're still Royal Guards, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:45.57,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,The Royal Guard only attacks adventurers \Nwhen they fight in a no-combat zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.66,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.87,0:05:51.46,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:54.08,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the negotiations aren't going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:57.01,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't gone well from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.01,0:05:59.08,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,How many times have we come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.44,0:06:02.09,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,The Kunie Clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:09.04,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they the clan that controls the banks? \NThe flow of money in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:11.55,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't only the banks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:14.22,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,They control the Royal Guard \Nsystem and all the lifelines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:19.55,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly, they also maintain the barriers \Nthat keep monsters out of towns.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:22.74,HUD1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(378,1)}Kinjou \N{\fs20}Race/ Half-Alv \NSuccessor, Lv. 50 \NKunie Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.81,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure it's impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:29.49,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It goes against an ancient treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:36.00,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Then, could we arrange \Nfinancing from the Kunie Clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.17,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:41.18,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,As you all know, the Round Table
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has purchased the Guild Building, \NCathedral, Trade Building,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:49.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,and several other facilities around the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:53.37,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We do this to ensure that they \Nwill not fall into enemy hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:54.63,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The costs are incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:07:01.02,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It all runs ten million gold a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:06.40,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't the cost of this building five million gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We're paying twice that a month?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:14.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's obvious that the Round \NTable is going to go broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:18.41,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to do festivals \Nor athletic meets anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.95,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,We have bigger problems than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:22.34,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Have you told the rest of the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:23.79,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:29.05,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it isn't a good idea for the \NRound Table to show weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.55,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You're concerned about the South?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:33.80,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Plant Hwyaden...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:36.81,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,There are rumors about them in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:41.06,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,This Plant Hwyaden guild is running \Na dictatorship in the South, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.15,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But it sounds like it's going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.32,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a friend in the South.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:47.15,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,He contacts me now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:50.02,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say that a dictatorship is always evil, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:54.83,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Crusty and Isaac aren't here now, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:08:00.46,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,The goblin army advance began with an \Nevent from when this was still a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.96,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Return of the Goblin King."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:07.42,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,The adventurers of Akihabara won \Na major victory at Zantleaf,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:12.19,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,and began an invasion of the main \Ngoblin camp at Seventh Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.68,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Crusty and Isaac went as commanders,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:23.30,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,and Karashin and Akaneya went to \Nsupport them as the rear guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:28.82,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see the South becoming \Nan immediate threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.32,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:39.38,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:43.23,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, we'll be having Nyanta's \Nspecial pumpkin feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:46.23,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's good, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:49.01,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,It's literally nothing but pumpkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:51.76,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, I want some meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.45,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Pumpkins are full of nutrients.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:57.41,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And they warm your body, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:09:00.63,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a picky eater. Please eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:02.02,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.52,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:04.77,SignB,T,0000,0000,0000,,Tenth-Place Prize
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:09.28,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,D.D.D. won, and Black Sword got second...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:11.61,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's amazing that we got tenth place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.65,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,So what's that, Minori?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:18.21,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Some guy I've never seen said it was a \Nparticipation prize, and insisted I take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:19.41,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,That's really scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:22.37,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's a goat-slime doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:26.47,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that one of those creepy-cute \Nitems I've heard about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:29.42,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what guys like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:35.84,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}In that sense, you're more mature... Calmer, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:34.67,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I see... It didn't work out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:36.43,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's Shiroe doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:41.99,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Minori, come to think of it, I didn't \Nsee Shiroe at today's festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:45.43,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it looks like he's busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:51.94,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I think his bad habit might be coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:57.24,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:04.13,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Now, give this memento to our guild master!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:05.18,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:06.47,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:08.69,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shiroe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.47,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Done working, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:10.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:11.96,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:13.44,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.46,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It was our tenth-place prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh... It's amazing, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:19.97,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe, here. I'm sure you're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:22.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:25.05,Default,Gi,0000,0000,0000,,Is your work really hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:26.60,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:30.26,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So, there's something I want to tell you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:36.09,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro, what did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:37.36,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Well, like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.86,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm planning to leave Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.13,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:45.04,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:51.04,SignB,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Just 30 days \N(or so) \Nuntil Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:47.17,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What will we do about Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:48.88,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a month from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What will we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.04,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:11:00.80,Location,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(315,1)\an9}Tearstone Mountains{\fs18}\NJapan Server \NOou \NField/ Monsters Present \NPVP Permitted \NSkill Use Permitted \NEntry Restrictions/ None \NExit Restrictions/ None
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.80,SignC,S,0000,0000,0000,,Top Secret
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.43,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.56,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:09.37,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:11.56,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Some snow, a little wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:13.29,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:14.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.07,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.19,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.33,0:11:26.10,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Don't you think you can tell me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:29.41,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's been ten days since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.17,Default - flashback,M,0000,0000,0000,,Leave Akihabara?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:34.82,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:41.43,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't told you all, but Akihabara \Nhas a problem right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.64,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.78,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it's the only way \Nto solve this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.64,Default - flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.72,Default - flashback,I,0000,0000,0000,,Then where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.07,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:12:00.65,Default - flashback,R,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd trust us more, guild master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:05.66,Default - flashback,M,0000,0000,0000,,There's a possibility that there are \NSouthern spies in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:10.24,Default - flashback,M,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know where information might leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:11.19,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.19,0:12:12.16,Default - flashback,I,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:14.85,Default - flashback,M,0000,0000,0000,,We need to keep our lips zipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:16.92,Default - flashback,H,0000,0000,0000,,What will you tell the Round Table?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:21.67,Default - flashback,M,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to tell Crusty, Isaac, and Soujirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:26.49,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,We believe in you, Shiroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:29.19,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:32.66,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Naotsugu, while I'm gone—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.66,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:36.18,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,A pitcher needs a catcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:37.94,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,An enchanter needs a guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.44,Default - flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:43.07,Default - flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:45.82,Default - flashback,A,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.72,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,You stay here in Akihabara, Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:53.82,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,I need to ask a favor that only you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:13:00.38,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you need money, why are \Nwe in these snowy mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:03.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get it by normal methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:06.42,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:07.78,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,A little?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:11.02,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,In all, about eighty trillion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:14.00,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eighty trillion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:15.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:18.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we got every gold piece owned \Nby every adventurer in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it probably wouldn't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:25.03,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really need all that \Nfor Akihabara's facilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:32.29,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Excuse me, Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:35.62,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Your guest is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.54,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you half-hidden?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:42.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right if I say it's been a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:45.05,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.27,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is Regan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.40,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,the Sage of Miral Lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:50.93,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:54.80,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,You see his name all the time in flavor text, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.94,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew he was such a dull-looking old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:13:59.38,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:00.94,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:04.59,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Kunie Clan's representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.20,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kinjou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.80,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:12.80,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored to meet a member of the Kunie Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.22,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The honor is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:18.36,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The representative of the adventurers, \Nthe great mage Shiroe,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:21.04,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,and Regan, the Sage of Miral Lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.71,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Even our great ancestors
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would never have imagined \Na meeting such as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:34.10,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,This wonderful meeting is enhanced \Neven further by your presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:35.59,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,The Kunie Clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.59,0:14:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious race that carries on the \Ntechnology of a magical civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:43.41,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,My heart swells with expectation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:44.57,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Expectation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:46.11,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.95,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe is, after all, a man full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:51.70,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I am pleased to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:56.74,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I called you here for an important reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:58.84,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You need money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:00.83,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Financing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:02.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:04.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I told you this in Akihabara, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.35,0:15:07.34,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,You chose this place for our meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you know it's where our village is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:13.22,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Regan told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:17.52,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,So Miral Lake has such records, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:21.99,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,With Regan's cooperation, I was able to determine
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:25.01,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,that the Kunie Clan's village is \Nnear the Tearstone Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:28.51,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,"I know where you live."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.73,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's no more than a threat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:31.57,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:37.04,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to accept a request from you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:38.53,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:40.54,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:43.79,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It goes against an ancient treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:49.51,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's just like what I found on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.40,0:15:55.75,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Banks in this world will neither \Nloan nor invest money outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:58.18,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,They'll repay the money they've been given.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:15:59.70,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:04.94,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the moneylender job class \Ndoesn't exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.87,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,And all the money
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:15.78,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,is gained by defeating monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:21.91,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,930)}The whole world has one common currency.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:29.34,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You can get money by defeating monsters, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:31.17,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:33.56,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And from treasure chests in dungeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:35.93,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, you'll get several \Nhundred gold pieces at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:39.43,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to the bravery of the adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:43.94,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't get funding from the Kunie Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.69,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,then why don't we get the money from the one
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.86,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,who puts it there, before he does so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:58.58,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro, you can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.34,0:17:02.34,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,When you defeat monsters, you earn money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:05.15,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's how a game works.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.33,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,But that isn't realistic at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:11.80,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,When{\i0} Elder Tale {\i1}was a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.48,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,there was a story about
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:18.00,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,an ancient, powerful magic device that \Nwould give reborn souls gold coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:21.39,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to use that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:24.35,Default - italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is there even such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:27.10,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And you believe that is possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:33.70,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Monster reincarnation can be \Nexplained via spirit theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:37.87,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,But who gives them the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:42.67,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I read every single ancient record in Miral Lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:46.20,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,And... I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:48.13,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,The Kunie Clan's gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:54.82,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,In the deepest depths of Palm,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:58.94,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,there is said to be a great whirlpool of gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:05.12,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,And the Sage of Miral Lake fifteen generations \Nago performed a sealing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.53,0:18:08.00,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I confirmed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:15.28,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's sealed with Miral Lake's technology, \Nbut breaking it won't be that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:18.52,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you were up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:23.74,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Then you will get your money \Nfrom this golden whirlpool?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:25.15,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:29.00,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,And you think this gold has something \Nto do with the Kunie Clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:31.00,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:37.01,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,So wouldn't getting your gold there \Nmean you'd be stealing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:40.91,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Does the Round Table wish to plunder it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:43.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I called you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:47.02,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to fight the Kunie Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:50.77,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,What would you use all that money for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:00.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If I explain,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:05.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,is there a chance you'll help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:10.95,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,None.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:13.29,Default,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,It goes against an ancient treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:25.06,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Shiroe talk to Kinjou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:29.31,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,He could've just taken the gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:33.28,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,For his goals, Shiroe will do whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.06,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:36.90,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's different when he wants to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:39.07,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.38,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.38,0:19:43.30,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't want to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:45.98,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But the way he talks isn't very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:47.08,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:50.46,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The guy from the Kunie Clan \Nis a big believer in secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:52.08,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And Shiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:58.26,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,When he's making a new contract or \Ndoing business with a new person,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:00.07,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,he wants everyone to reveal all their secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:03.84,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,so he knows where they're coming from and \Nhe can tell them everything about himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:06.48,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to make sure their interests align,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:08.93,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,and then show them he's a good \Npartner who can be trusted!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:13.04,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Were you a merchant, Naotsugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:15.05,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I was in sales, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:16.20,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Sales?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:19.51,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a negotiation skill or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:23.21,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I wish he'd open up more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:36.56,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think he meant by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.30,Default - flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,Then let us meet there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.73,0:20:45.26,Default - flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The meandering river and the \Nforgotten underground garden,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:48.36,Default - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,where gold that appears from the \Nvoid disappears into the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:53.38,Default - flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,But you will need the company \Nof many in order to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:56.69,Default - flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,How will you reach the spring \Nin the deepest depths?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:21:03.22,Default - flashback,Gu,0000,0000,0000,,The Kunie Clan's answer will depend \Nupon the result of your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:06.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The company of many...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:11.83,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,He clearly means there'll be \Na large-scale battle, a raid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:17.44,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,In the depths of Palm, there's a raid zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:21.13,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And unless we clear it, we can't have the gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:23.20,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expected it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.87,0:21:26.16,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That means we'll need people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:26.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:29.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't bring the Round Table members.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:32.43,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The South is watching them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:35.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want them to know what we're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:37.11,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:40.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I know a place we could go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.91,0:21:50.00,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:21:59.38,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,I failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,0:22:03.54,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,I was naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:07.41,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't trust them enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.47,0:22:18.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You were defeated, Akatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.06,0:22:21.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:24.49,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:26.85,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.80,0:22:34.70,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a heck of a Christmas Eve, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.85,0:24:08.50,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,We land to the far north.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:12.43,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,There, we find a man whose name \Nis William Massachusetts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.70,0:24:15.47,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The guild master of a proud fighting guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.47,0:24:18.27,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,A man who once broke off relations with Shiroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.27,0:24:21.02,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,And another... Demikas,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.02,0:24:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a man whose life Shiroe once took.
